{"type": "article", "id": 14855, "title": "高帮防水运动鞋", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-14T07:09:33Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 51, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000311hcOnrQwIFSP1qvoD.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这款高帮防水的运动鞋非常适合即将到来的秋天，在鞋身采用来自英国的高密度L27 Ventile 布料，很透气，而定制的鞋舌在防止水渗入的同时也能让脚保持舒适。为了保证质量，这款鞋专门在日本的一家有140年做鞋历史的工厂加工。有海军蓝配黑色鞋带和橄榄绿配米色鞋带两种，售价242美元。<a href=\"http://www.contextclothing.com/brands/the-hill-side/sn6-315-all-weather-high-top-sneakers-navy\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142251yJ3C0aLuvXe1drBK.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142252LJV8I7RbklUpQ0Og.jpg\" width=\"768\" height=\"768\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142253DiKOTRwPNLH9dFC8.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142253So6kZhzaMvKUH4Fc.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}